{"tid":1572184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【ChiNazi戰線】全球清算共黨卧底正式開始 澳洲華裔女議員Gladys Liu被爆共黨背景","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T05:12:39.000Z","uid":158255,"like":483,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"14a8487757592d3d571bca1d8c7844fce2b9bc83","tid":1572184,"uid":158255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"呢2日係Twitter睇到單澳洲新聞，大概講個緊澳洲華裔女議員Gladys Liu被爆同共黨有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNBUk49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNBUk49.jpg&h=25b727ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-09-15/gladys-lui-united-front-work-department/11511028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2019-09-15%2Fgladys-lui-united-front-work-department%2F11511028&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=875604b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.abc.net.au/news/2019-09-15/gladys-lui-united-front-work-department/11511028</a><br />\n/Gladys Liu is in hot water over her alleged association with the <span style=\"color: red;\">United Front Work Department</span> of the Chinese Communist Party./<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.com.au/finance/work/leaders/sam-clench-the-backlash-against-gladys-lius-trainwreck-interview-shrouds-a-broader-problem/news-story/51ab448d4143964ece97b2d3829481a5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Ffinance%2Fwork%2Fleaders%2Fsam-clench-the-backlash-against-gladys-lius-trainwreck-interview-shrouds-a-broader-problem%2Fnews-story%2F51ab448d4143964ece97b2d3829481a5&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDrtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=ca9d0458\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.com.au/finance/work/leaders/sam-clench-the-backlash-against-gladys-lius-trainwreck-interview-shrouds-a-broader-problem/news-story/51ab448d4143964ece97b2d3829481a5</a><br />\n跟住又係人地個live 訪問被人問南海問題問到口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n/Bolt: &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">Can I just hear you say it, that you support the Australian government&rsquo;s position that the theft of the South China Sea by China is unlawful? Is it unlawful, yes or no?</span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nLiu: &ldquo;Well as I said, I want to make sure that Australians&rsquo; interests were put first and foremost and if it&rsquo;s going to affect our trade or our air travelling, then that is something that I would not support.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nBolt: &ldquo;Well in fact, it does affect our trade. Sixty per cent of it goes through that sea.... <span style=\"color: red;\">Why are you not going along with that?</span>&rdquo;/<br />\n <br />\n個主持人直線抽擊 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問閘大大係咪dictator唔敢答</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBolt: &ldquo;Gladys, Gladys, excuse me. You were born in Hong Kong. At the moment, <span style=\"color: red;\">you have seen in your home place people in their millions at times, 1.7 million, in their millions, protesting against what China is doing there and you don&rsquo;t have any opinion on Xi Jinping</span>?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nLiu: &ldquo;OK, so if you want to talk about China, let me just tell you one thing. I was born in Hong Kong and I never stepped into China before I came to Australia. I had the Hong Kong ID card. I never held a Chinese passport. I had the Hong Kong travelling document and then I&rsquo;ve got the Australian passport. In terms of Hong Kong, it is very, very sad for anyone to see what has happened.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nBolt: &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">But Gladys, a simple question. Is Xi Jinping a dictator</span>?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nLiu: &ldquo;That is not a question for me to answer, but I can tell you about Hong Kong. It is very &hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nBolt: &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t want to know about Hong Kong. <span style=\"color: red;\">I am asking you about Xi Jinping, the dictator of communist China, and you don&rsquo;t have an opinion about him.</span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nLiu: &ldquo;I do have an opinion, but <span style=\"color: red;\">I&rsquo;m not going to use the word dictator. He is in their system an elected chairman or president, they call it, for China</span>.&rdquo;//<br />\n<br />\n有冇澳洲巴絲補充下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩錯屌細力啲"},{"pid":"28219773e3faa0b2a49ec904b9abaa786de4d348","tid":1572184,"uid":32187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f5db679104885d1fa03427b64819df7623f0d38","tid":1572184,"uid":100999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"350d748f86d977da8bed5bd1b4cd62223bec4f8e","tid":1572184,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"有無中文媒體COVER?"},{"pid":"e727a6344d1536802c5269e6ccfc5ce72a4bcebb","tid":1572184,"uid":218288,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"個澳洲總理仲要撐鳩個間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8fd6ba908eb52442421bb1893cc3a9edaa473f","tid":1572184,"uid":58335,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"e727a6344d1536802c5269e6ccfc5ce72a4bcebb","tid":1572184,"uid":218288,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:25:27.000Z","msg":"個澳洲總理仲要撐鳩個間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09